<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DJ League - Home</title>
    <style>
        /* General Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #0a0b0d;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0;
        }

        h1, h2, p {
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1c1c1c, #ff4d4d);
            border-bottom: 3px solid #ff4d4d;
        }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 4rem;
                text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
            }

        /* Card Container */
        .card-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px; /* Reduced gap between cards */
            flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allow wrapping if necessary */
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        /* Card Styling */
        .card {
            background-color: #ff4d4d;
            color: #fff;
            width: 150px; /* Reduced width */
            height: 200px; /* Reduced height */
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.5);
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            /* Card Hover Effect */
            .card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.7);
                background-color: #1c1c1c;
                color: #ff4d4d;
            }

            /* Card Title */
            .card h3 {
                font-size: 1.2rem; /* Reduced font size */
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e1e, #003366);
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .about h2 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                letter-spacing: 2px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                color: #ff4d4d;
            }

            .about p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
                margin: 0 auto;
                max-width: 900px;
            }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #1c1c1c;
            color: #ff4d4d;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid #ff4d4d;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Hover Animations */
        .card:focus {
            outline: none;
        }

        .about p {
            color: #ccc;
        }

        /* Gradient Background */
        .gradient-background {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1c1c1c, #ff4d4d);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientAnimation 8s ease infinite;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <div class="gradient-background">

        <!-- Header -->
        <header>
            <h1>Welcome to DJ League</h1>
            <p>The Ultimate Gaming Tournament of 2024</p>
            <p>Compete, Conquer, and Dominate the World of Esports</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Navigation Section (Cards) -->
        <section class="card-container">
            <a href="/Details" class="card">
                <h3>Details</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/Games" class="card">
                <h3>Games</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/Matches" class="card">
                <h3>Matches</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/PricePools" class="card">
                <h3>Prize Pools</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/Regions" class="card">
                <h3>Regions</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/Teams" class="card">
                <h3>Teams</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/Tournaments" class="card">
                <h3>Tournaments</h3>
            </a>
        </section>

        <!-- About Section -->
        <section class="about">
            <h2>About DJ League</h2>
            <p>
                DJ League is not just another esports tournament — it's the heart of competitive gaming. With cutting-edge technology, high stakes, and a global stage for players to compete, DJ League is the pinnacle of esports excellence. Players from across the world will clash in thrilling, high-octane tournaments to prove who is the best.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 DJ League. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
